<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She received the award for Best New Artist on Sunday night with a somewhat meandering acceptance speech.</p>

<p>And before that, rising star Doja Cat performed her hit tracks Like That and Say So during the MTV Video Music Awards in a skintight glowing bodysuit that gave off the impression that she was nude.</p>

<p>The Rules songstress, 24, looked at once space-age and reptilian in her performance costume, which featured metallic scales and glowing genitalia.</p>

<p>On Sunday: Rising star Doja Cat performed her hit tracks Like That and Say So during the MTV Video Music Awards in a skintight glowing bodysuit that gave off the impression she was nude</p>

<p>She also wore a mane of phosphorescent green hair that flowed back over her shoulders.</p>

<p>The controversial singer delivered her raps and rhymes with an insistence reminiscent of Nicki Minaj, as she engaged in interesting dance moves that seemed robotic.  </p>

<p>Doja was aided in her stage show by backup dancers in iridescent metallic suits complete with CDC-recommended face coverings. </p>

<p>Other dancers looked even wackier, in dark blue bodysuits adorned with impossibly long thorns protruding from the back. </p>

