<p>And later, Doja accepted her Best New Artist accolade in a somewhat tamer getup, that nonetheless featured an endlessly long braid of hair. </p>

<p>For her victorious moment, the Boss Bitch diva donned a tasseled bright crimson minidress.</p>

<p>The garment boasted a deeply plunging neckline, but the focus remained Cat's braid, which skimmed her ankles. </p>

